Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:04.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,This girl is Kouyama Mitsuki.\NShe's twelve and dreams of becoming a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:07.60,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But unfortunately, she only has\N one year left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,We, the Shinigami, were sent to make sure that her destiny did not change, but...{afk: We, the Shinigami, were sent \Nto tell her about her inevitable fate, but... // No, they weren't supposed to *tell* her, because humans aren't supposed to be able to see or hear Shinigami at all! }
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:14.28,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Today, she became an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...and she performed incredibly at the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:19.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Doesn't this mean {\i1}we're{\i0} changing her destiny!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.08,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I wonder what's going to happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:23.50,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.12,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(352,462)}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.02,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,{\pos(352,462)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,This is {\i1}your{\i0} fault, Takuto!\NDidn't that girl pass the audition!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:14.94,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Man... I was surprised, too. \NI never thought she'd get chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:17.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Don't act like it's someone else's problem!{Don't talk like that about other people's lives! // wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.30,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Stop being so shrill, Meroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.94,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Don't tell me you've forgotten what our purpose here is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:29.05,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,To make sure that nothing changes \Nthe fact that she has one year left to live, right?{To make sure that when her one year is up...\N...she won't refuse to come with us, right? // wrong!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:30.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Then why should it matter... {}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.89,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...if she passed the audition or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.65,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Ah! I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.88,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.57,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,She was willing to return to the house with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.35,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Now that she's become a singer,\N it'll be a pain if we have to follow her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:46.52,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Plus, you used the Dead Arts on a human like her...{Plus, you let a human like her learn the truth... // I'm pretty sure says shininjutsu (shinin = dead person / corpse, jutsu = arts/techniques/skills), not shinjitsu (truth) here. A more subtle mishear on afk's part, but a mishear nonetheless ~Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.47,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...and even turned her into a 16-year-old!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.77,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I won't forgive you for a stunt like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.96,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.28,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I was just thinking that you Shinigami seem to be so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:02:59.88,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.48,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I-Is that how it looks? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:03.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,We are the Shinigami Duo \Nwho silence the tears of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.72,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...Negi Ramen! {note here}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.80,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm really grateful for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh? Oh... it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.84,Default-Overlap (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,By the way, what was that song you sang... {}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.84,Default (Plain),,62,62,0,Dialogue,What is this!? Why am I the only one doing it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.72,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...at your audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.89,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,My father was a musician, \Nand that was one of his songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.39,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.24,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.76,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:35.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I feel like I might have heard it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Don't think that you've become an adult just because you passed the audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.97,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,W-When I'm in this body, I'm all grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.98,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hmm... so then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:47.62,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Meroko! Stop harassing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:52.90,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Oh, but I can't go home like this.\N Can you turn me back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.04,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh? Oh yeah. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Amazing! I turned back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yep. Your chest returned to normal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,P-Please don't stare at me like that. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:14.77,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Geez... you're so stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.56,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.54,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Do you really plan on becoming a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.48,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I promised, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,My promise with... Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun? Wait, who is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Your sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:30.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What!? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.35,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,H-He's not my sweetheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.88,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,So that means he's somebody you admire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:44.76,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Until two years ago,\N I was living at an orphanage.{afk: Two years ago, I entered \Na treatment center for the ill.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:48.94,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I was with Eichi-kun the whole time, until Grandma took me in.{afk: While Grandma was traveling abroad, I stayed there with Eichi-kun. // *nothing* about "traveling abroad" in there}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.84,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,He told me his feelings, \Nbut before I could answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.76,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...he left for America because of\N circumstances beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:01.23,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),No, no! Don't go, Eichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:05.15,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Don't cry, Mitsuki. America isn't that far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:06.89,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.82,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Let's make a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:13.12,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Until we meet again, \Nwe'll work hard to reach our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.82,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),I'll become an astronomer.\NAnd you'll become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.35,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Mitsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.74,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),...I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:44.19,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Even though we'll be apart,\N I'll look for the moon in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.66,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),That's why you have to shine even brighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.64,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),...so that I can find you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.46,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),More... and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.50,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,And since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.83,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:02.83,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Haven't you had any contact with him since then? \NLike a letter, or a phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.64,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, that's the problem. I have no idea \Nhow to get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.30,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But if I accomplish my dream\N of becoming a singer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:11.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...my name might even reach \Nsomewhere as far as America.{And once again, Japanese record labels' delusions that they can be hits in America are manifested. ~Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.43,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Then I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.77,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...that Eichi-kun will notice me... maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.52,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You've put your whole heart into this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Somewhat, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What is it, Takuto?\NYou're making such a frightening face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:29.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I thought you honestly wanted to become a singer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...but it was all for a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.04,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's just impure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:42.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,If you don't have pure intentions of becoming a singer, you can't become a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.50,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You'd better quit singing immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,W-Why are you saying something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.36,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:48.93,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What's so wrong with doing it because of a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:49.63,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Everything! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:52.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'll... work really hard at singing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,No matter how hard you work, you'll always be irresponsible about it on some level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.17,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I would never be irresponsible about singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.34,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's right! What part of this is impure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What part of doing it for a guy {\i1}is{\i0} pure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:10.64,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Besides, doesn't it seem strange \Nthat he's neglected you for two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.28,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You've been dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.68,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,He's probably living it up \Nwith another girl over there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.75,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,E-Eichi-kun wouldn't ever do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.60,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Why can't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's because... it's Eichi-kun, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.51,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hmph. That's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.71,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hey! Cut it out, Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.06,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Anyway, I won't ever cooperate with someone like you again.{afk:Anyways, someone as disrespectful of singing as you... //wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.59,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Because you don't respect singing!{...will never sing again! // wrong, ni do to kyouryoku shinai = will never cooperate again -- this was re-arranged into the previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.68,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,W-Wait... Takuto. Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.52,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Come on, Takuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.80,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Geez... why's he so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:46.79,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...what kind of person would interfere with fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.61,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,The one most likely to interfere\N with someone's fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.57,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...is the person that human loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.57,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'll have to pay special attention to this "Eichi" character.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.14,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Just what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.49,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,When I told you that you shouldn't audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I wasn't trying to be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.13,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's impossible because of\N your body's current condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Are you finished now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.03,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.01,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But now you understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.98,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That you'll be unable to sing for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.31,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Ah... no, I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.07,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.72,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:40.15,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),I can't tell him what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.65,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),But I wonder if he would believe that I transformed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:47.04,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),...or about the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.00,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What do you mean by "made it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It couldn't be that... you passed the audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.19,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.47,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),It's no good. There's no way he'd ever believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.82,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um... I meant modeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.11,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Oh... modeling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.66,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, modeling is all well and good, but don't do anything irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:06.69,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.89,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,By the way, what'd you do for the application?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.61,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Did you write your grandma's name\N under "Guardian"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:15.61,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Did you put {\i1}my{\i0} name down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,F-Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.14,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,We'll keep it a secret from your grandma, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.37,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I-Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.26,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sure. I understand your feelings, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:32.84,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's for Eichi-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.55,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Y-Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:47.31,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sneaking out of the house without saying a word is simply improper. {afk: You are not allowed to leave this house.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:51.01,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What's more, you had your doctor\N take you to the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Your disobedience knows no bounds! {afk: "...you have no shame!" // Literal TL here is "there is a limit to impudence", but there's not enough time in the line to do a good rendering of that. This versiion works imo. ~Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:56.76,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),An amusement park? So that's where we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.02,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.74,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.75,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Next time, a simple apology will not suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.62,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Please excuse yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:11.72,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:18.57,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wait a minute. What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.63,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What {\i1}is{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.97,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.88,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,From... um... {\alpha&HFF}the crane game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.02,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,From... um... the crane game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.09,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.58,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:44.07,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What a shrill old hag. I was worried she'd tell you to throw me away. {afk: Such an annoying grandma...\NShe kept going on and on... // wrong!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But this means that you're one step closer to your dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:48.31,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:52.79,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,So, what kind of guy is Eichi-kun?\NIf you've got a picture, you've gotta show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.25,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.72,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wow! He's a pretty good-looking guy.\NHow old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.98,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,We're six years apart, so he'd be eighteen now. {Isn't this statutory raep, even in Japan?? Well, unless she's FullMoon!Mitsuki, that is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.74,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,So this picture was taken \Nwhen Eichi-kun was sixteen? {mis-styled as Mitsuki in original afk subs}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:11.15,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sooo cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:21.42,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,1031,1,\3c&H252525&\4c&H000000&)}Besides, doesn't it seem strange \Nthat he's neglected you for two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:23.49,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),{\t(1179,0,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}You've been dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.95,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.35,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun's the only one who wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.74,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,So this is where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.26,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:59.43,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, that means I have nowhere left to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.82,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That girl looks like she wants to be alone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.12,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You upset her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:08.04,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:11.00,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's all your fault, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,She's down because you told her\N that she'd been dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, it's a perfectly natural assumption. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:24.68,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Besides, in this day and age, it's weird to carry a torch for a guy who's already dumped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.39,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's {\i1}weird{\i0}, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.60,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.09,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Just like randomly busting out the Dead Arts.{afk: Always avoiding the truth... // tsukau is definitely not "avoid", which is another reason why I think this and line 60 use "shininjutsu". "Using the truth" doesn't make much sense. ~Z }
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,The old Takuto never would've done that.{afk: ...you haven't changed at all, Takuto. // completely opposite meaning -- if he hadn't changed at all, why would she think that the act in line 266 was weird?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:37.48,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,S-Stupid. It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.28,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I-Isn't this our duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sure, I may have "assumed" she was dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:46.23,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's just that in general, long-distance relationships tend not to work...{afk: "I was just saying that as a general\N observation... I didn't state it very well." // wrong! -- "enkyori ren'ai" was not properly heard against Meroko's overlapping line, so the original line is a combination of the begnining and end of the actual dialogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.39,Default-Overlap (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),{\i1}Just as I thought... something's amiss.{\i0} {}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Usually, in situations like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.45,Default-Overlap (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),{\i1}Takuto is mine!{\i0} {}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.25,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:58.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:02.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yep. I'll read your fortune for today. Pick a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:05.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Okay. Um, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:11.96,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wow! That's great! Today's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.69,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yep. Super lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,The lucky word is... {\alpha&HFF&}shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.65,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,The lucky word is... shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Something good will definitely happen.\NCome on, let's go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:24.61,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Grandma's out today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.58,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Ah, but I have to ask Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.88,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Do you need something, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um, I'd like to go out shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.40,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But Madam said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.12,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I wonder what Grandma would say \Nif she learned that you...{afk:If Grandma learns that you were secretly listening to music...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...were secretly listening to music?{afk:...I wonder what she'll say?} {Nice to know our cute innocent protagonist has already mastered the art of blackmail.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You might be scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:02.27,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Where are they going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.54,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,If Meroko's going along, \Nthen I'll just let her handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:37.79,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Mitsuki-chan, this might take awhile. \N Can you wait at the usual place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.44,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sure. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.94,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Then... then... just wait a little while, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.49,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,There's somewhere I want to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.76,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um, this might take awhile, \Nso can you wait outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.66,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Shinigami use the restroom too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.80,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,She left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.09,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,She should've known I'd have a reason for suggesting this little excursion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.01,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Mero-Mero Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.62,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's mine! It's mine, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.75,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I wonder what that "good thing" is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.27,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's been a while, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.35,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.23,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.69,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,T-This can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Oh, it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.60,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),A real lie, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.74,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Once your wish to see Eichi-kun is granted,\N you won't need to become a singer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:27.05,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Plus, once your true love is on the scene,\N Takuto will give up on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.66,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I-I'm dreaming, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.22,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,This is no dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:38.97,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Even though I went to America,\N I never forgot about you, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:43.94,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's why I hurried back to Japan\N once I heard you'd become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:47.63,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But who told you that I'd become a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:52.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Who told me, you ask? It was \Ns-someone I know in the record business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's an amazing coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It was more than a coincidence; it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.27,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.82,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,By the way, Eichi-kun... what's with that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I guess living in America must've changed my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:08.64,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Since America's so vast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You're so funny. {rt?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.30,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.07,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,W-What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.96,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,There's something I have to apologize to you for, Eichi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:23.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun, I... doubted you. {afk: I... for your sake... I sang...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I thought you might have forgotten about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.64,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What? That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.64,Default-Overlap (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm very sorry. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:35.31,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Mitsuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:38.02,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Will you still... like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:40.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.57,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:46.21,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Back then, I couldn't give you a proper answer, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:51.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.59,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm also... in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.01,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.80,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm... I'm... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.16,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Eichi-kun? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.55,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Shinigami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.86,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That isn't Eichi. It's Meroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.42,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:13.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:17.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,We Shinigami are able to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.36,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Is... that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.75,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,There's no way Eichi-kun... would be here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.42,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.59,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Is something wrong, Mitsuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,No. There's nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:37.67,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Your face looks pale. Come on, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.69,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That was horrible! You've really done it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.23,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It seemed like a good idea at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.97,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What was so "good" about it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You were just toying with \Na person's sincere ambitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.71,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...and their pure feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.50,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You think an apology will solve this? {Because it's too late to apologize, it's toooo laaaaateeee}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.24,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:01.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:05.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,"Pure"... didn't you just say that they were impure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.95,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Huh? I said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.13,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You did!{You said it!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.70,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,"What part of doing it for a guy {\i1}is{\i0} pure?"\N ...or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.02,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That... was about becoming a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Those issues have nothing to do with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.71,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I guess what I did {\i1}was{\i0} pretty cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:24.24,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But you don't even {\i1}know{\i0} Eichi,\N and yet you said he dumped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.97,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What about {\i1}you{\i0}, Takuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.64,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Don't you think that your words hurt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.30,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That stuff I said about you being dumped was just my own opinion. Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.41,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,It's just a possibility. No... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:51.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.66,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,No. I was also at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.92,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,If I really believed in Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.10,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...I wouldn't be worried,\N no matter what anybody told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.51,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's why I won't be confused anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.89,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I... love Eichi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.46,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But I love singing just as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.68,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,If I love him, then I have to believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I have to believe in him with all my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.86,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,or else my dream will never come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:21.07,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,These feelings will never be impure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.03,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Well, that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.65,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Accomplish as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.74,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'll work to fulfill your dream over the next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.50,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.96,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,As long as I'm around, \Nmy blood will always be inside you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.08,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...I'll always be able to transform you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.17,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,When I'm not with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:44.63,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,use this whistle to call me. I'll fly to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.85,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Thank you, Shinigami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.81,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Enough with the "Shinigami-san". Call me Takuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.33,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Okay. Thank you, Takuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.31,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Could it be that my trick has backfired on me? {alternate suggestion: "Have I been hoisted with my own petard? // probably too obscure a phrase, and doesn't really fit a kids' show}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.78,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Ah, Bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.99,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.24,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,T-Thank me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:05.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.91,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Because today was really my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.53,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You changed into Eichi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:13.82,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,...to give me courage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:16.37,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.15,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Why did the bunny apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.34,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:26.15,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'll never do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:30.01,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),Eichi-kun, I made it through the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.65,Default-Italic (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue (Thought),I'll definitely go see you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:08.36,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Takuto! There's an emergency... an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:11.03,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Her manager is coming to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:12.15,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,You can't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:13.20,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.45,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Mitsuki's established Dr. Wakaouji as her guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:20.54,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Wait... that physician only knows her as a 12-year-old.{afk: Wait... That person won't recognize her when she's twelve... // mishearing of "shujii", and a misunderstanding of the <something> shika <negative verb> structure}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.71,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,But the manager's expecting to meet her\N as a 16-year-old, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.87,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,What are we going to do, Takuto!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.67,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Ahhhhh... I don't know anymore!\NWhatever happens, happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:30.38,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Next time on Full Moon wo Sagashite:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:32.30,Default (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,The Manager Arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:33.64,Default-Sync (Plain),,0,0,0,Dialogue,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.39,OP 1 Eng (Plain),,0,0,0,Karaoke,The road to love is far too long for me.
